snippet.title: Judge ENDS Amber Heard - She is going to PRISON!
snippet.description:
💙 Judge ENDS Amber Heard - She is going to PRISON!
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's court case made a significant unexpected development when Johnny Depp recorded a maligning claim against his ex. He asserted that she lied in court, yet in addition that she was oppressive toward him. Notwithstanding all this, he filed a defamation suit against her.
